extends Object
    Kurento Media Builder base interface. Builds a <T> object, either synchronously using build() or asynchronously using buildAsync(org.kurento.client.Continuation<T>)

        public void buildAsync​(Continuation<T> continuation)
        Builds an object asynchronously using the builder design pattern.

        The continuation will have Continuation.onSuccess(F) called when the object is ready, or Continuation.onError(java.lang.Throwable) if an error occurs
        Parameters:
